const projects = [
  {
    id: 1,
    title: 'Asset Track',
    description: 'This web application lets you track your investements all conveniently in one place.'
               + 'It was built using Python for the backend and the frontend with plain vanilla Javascript and of'
               + ' course HTML and CSS. I would love for you to check it out and please give me some feedback!',
    image: '../static/images/projects/asset_track.png',
    link: 'https://still-cove-11137.herokuapp.com',
    button: 'Website',
  },
    {
      id: 2,
      title: 'CoVid Simulation',
      description: 'In the time during quarantine I decided to build a little CoVid-19 simulation which should '
                 + 'highlight the importance of social distancing. ',
      image: '../static/images/projects/covid.png',
      link: 'https://github.com/rafaelwanner/CoVid-19-Simulation',
      button: 'Repository',
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      title: 'Snake Game',
      description: 'My personal implementation of the infamous snake game. I build it using the module Pygame.'
                + ' My personal record is 30 points. Try and beat me.',
      image: '../static/images/projects/snake.png',
      link: 'https://github.com/rafaelwanner/Snake',
      button: 'Repository',
    }
];

export default projects;
